Good times continue for the U.S. defense industry, as Pentagon budget money continues to roll-in
March 26, 2019
THE MIL & AERO COMMENTARY – Remember last year when we considered the 2019 Pentagon budget request to be one of the biggest of all time? Well fast-forward a year, and the 2020 military budget request is even bigger.
